page.title: 16LOCAL NATURAL HISTORY
page.content: MORE THAN HALF OF OUR AREA IS ON WEALD CLAY WHICH SUPPORTS WOODLAND AND FARM- LAND - ARABLE AND PASTURE. TO THE EAST IS ALLUVIUM -GRASSLAND.
